    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. The exterior has some noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and the paint is beginning to fade on the roof and hood. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it will eventually need attention for a slow oil leak and some suspension wear that causes a slight rattle over bumps. The interior is generally clean but has some staining on the upholstery and a cracked dashboard. It\u2019s a solid choice for someone looking for affordable transportation who doesn't mind a few cosmetic and mechanical imperfections.",
